{"tid":2479140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李宇軒肯撚定係仆街25仔金手指","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:11:59.000Z","uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2934eb72c09c57644ed424dfd429dc09fe535452","tid":2479140,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:02:51.000Z","msg":"頭先個post標題開得唔好<br />\n<br />\n佢個妹del account<br />\n啲人就話搵到佢所以完成歷史使命咪刪除<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\non9咁就知佢喺神秘組嘅時候就已經del啦<br />\n點會去到見完面先del<br />\n<br />\n仲有如果真係比港共打壓逼佢做金手指，佢個妹就梗係保留account繼續抗衡政府啦，總之我相信正常人遇到咁嘅事就一定會保留個account繼續每日更新阿哥嘅資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計我話李宇軒一定係自動申請做金手指，如果唔係佢個妹就唔會而家避風頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">時間會證明我係啱，LM等睇兒登仔屌我之後炒車，等睇其他手足爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9e92b83bb8886e25d08f2d64c3d60c7f9c736c79","tid":2479140,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"鍾共打手勿回<br />\n<br />\n連登培生培心會員討論區（1）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2476780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2476780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓豬簡介：<br />\n- 用小米機<br />\n- 用支那 APP<br />\n- 用 HK01 賣港 APP<br />\n- 鍾共培生會粉絲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用小米機(仲要唔係一千以下)反共講出嚟知唔知醜<br />\n畀埋錢支企賺撐共就有你份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmemgqePMhWydUc2rxg7daoYiPvjaeRZpA8TfMhXCexT3Z?filename=RSsFtA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSsFtA2.png&h=c68c0e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17c367e487be6f437082fe997d1ec6c09800d843","tid":2479140,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"講多樣<br />\n冚家鏟樓主刻意大量cap 殘體文嚟做文化滲透<br />\n<br />\n微博有品蔥手足俾人拉咗 仲要畀支共公審<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2478215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2478215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中共黨員警察舉報領導貪污後被追殺 無奈拍片留下遺言：我知道躲得了初一躲不了15<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2477609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2477609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"26110589ee3ec301034d86264e1961107550fd7e","tid":2479140,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/20210402-2471976-3-實名反共-費事啲人話我用小米係五毛.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Ffollowing%2F391580%2F20210402-2471976-3-%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%B1-%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%8B%E5%95%B2%E4%BA%BA%E8%A9%B1%E6%88%91%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E4%BF%82%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B.png&h=e8070c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸住部小米機話反共，人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n仲要係<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">小米10</span></strong></span>，大把外國牌子平機唔揀<br />\n揀部幾千蚊嘅小米機畀錢中共賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小米心諗最好全部反共嘅都買佢部機佢就 fat fat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有 $$$ 又有 data 送中一網打盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員編號：#391580<br />\n會員註冊日期：2021/2/3<br />\n入 LIST 原因：屢次自爆用小米機，用過嚟 check 自己嘢，仲有一堆支那 APP 不能盡錄，仲要係鍾共粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=65c1ea3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/39